Name: Die, A.I.
About the game: You must stay alive in this horror/puzzle space adventure. Survive the vengeful A.I system that has taken over the ship and killed everyone else onboard. Use your limited oxygen supply and cunning to overcome the failing systems and A.I created booby traps. Explore the ship...and don't die. The game currently includes the first chapter. Any future chapters will also cost $2.99 and will be in the form of DLC.
